                                                        <td style="padding-left:40px;">
                                                            <p style="color:#fff; font-size:13px; margin:0;"><b>Congratulations!…</b></p><span style="font-size:15px; color:#fff;">Your booking is confirmed and the e-ticket will be emailed to you shortly.</span>
